stanford mobile phone orchestra audience participation concert stanford mobile phone orchestra as part of the fall 2010 ccrma concert presents mopho 2.0 an audience participation concert of music for iphones and ipads participate now for converge 2.0 7pm thursday november 18 2010 ccrma stage stanford university 660 lomita dr stanford ca 94035 map free and open to public the stanford mobile phone orchestra mopho presents an evening of all new works of mobile electronic chamber music for iphones and laptop orchestra each piece will engage the audience actively as part of the performance featuring works and performances by jorge herrera nick bryan jieun oh ge wang spencer salazar nick kruge luke dahl and carr wilkerson read more about mopho here and here follow us on twitter and facebook directed by ge wang jieun oh jorge herrera and nick bryan mopho ccrma music stanford
